title: John Shuttleworth Collection
description:
A collection of John Shuttleworth material. John Shuttleworth is the (geniusly gentle) comic creation of Graeme Fellows, and features most on UK&#039;s BBC Radio 4, the birthplace of much comic talent. The folders are:

: Christmas Special

: John Shuttleworth and Family

: Radio Shuttleworth, Series One and Two

: Seven Songs By Sunset

: The Shuttleworths, Series One, Two, Three, Four
